OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNew dads find safe space   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffor postnatal support      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, New fathers, who struggled with mental 
OL,6, health issues after the births of their
OL,7, babies, are encouraging other men with 
OL,8, symptoms to seek help.                 
OL,10,FNial Sands realised "something was not 
OL,11,Fright" after the arrival of his baby   
OL,12,Fboy, 11 months ago.                    
OL,14,FHe now attends Dad's Voice in          
OL,15,FBallymena, County Antrim, a group that 
OL,16,Fprovides a safe space for fathers, who 
OL,17,Fneed support through parenting.        
OL,19,F"It's nice to know it's not just you   
OL,20,Ffeeling the pressure," he said.        
